Install
	
	url containing the install image
		url --url="url"

	repo: find packages that you want
		repo --repo="name" --baseUrl=http://...
		
	force text-mode install
		text
		
	

Device and Partition

	remove partitions before creating them during install
		clearpart
		
	specify size, format, and name of a partition
		part ...
		
	automate the last step
		autopart
		
	don't let anaconda modify your disk
		ignoredisk --drives=
		
	required: where do I install the bootloader?
		bootloader --location=... --boot-drive=...
		
	create lvm groups and volume
		volgroup ...
		logvol ...
		
There are many others that I will not memorize. Reference RHEL docs for the kickstart commands.



